###
To add a new font:

1) Copy font files to the directory

    fonts/

2) Match the file name with the font family name in the

    scripts/utils/fop_cfg.py
    (FONTS_INFO)

3) Run

    make fop_cfg

Alternatively

1) Copy the font files to the directory

    fonts/

2) Edit manually

    config/fop.xml

Details can be read here:

https://xmlgraphics.apache.org/fop/2.6/fonts.html

###
To find information about the fonts used in PDF file, use pdffonts
utility from the poppler-utils package

$ sudo apt-get install poppler-utils
$ pdffonts myfile.pdf
